{"tid":837042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［颱風追擊］1825號 康妮 （熱帶擾動）94W","createTime":"2018-09-26T05:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T12:54:57.000Z","uid":206416,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3de2cb72646163bb5860d13ae3af568cb741d603","tid":837042,"uid":206416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"將會命名［康妮］是由柬埔寨提供，指傳說中一位美女。<br />\n<br />\n10月5日歐洲中期預測會進入南海，有機會威脅廣東沿岸。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/133135_e0af331c729b59c8df7836e9a7323e9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F133135_e0af331c729b59c8df7836e9a7323e9f.png&h=35ef8058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/133649_a4989d7172d31d6e867ac85fcabb797b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F133649_a4989d7172d31d6e867ac85fcabb797b.png&h=5c38e400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源：觀氣象看天氣<br />\n<br />\n由於時間尚遠，存在極多可能性，秋颱特別難預測，歡迎各位在此發表，延伸討論。"},{"pid":"e366dc1f7f460d3289cfb558bf8a35f76a7dbcb0","tid":837042,"uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"諸葛神數測字算命<br />\n您輸入的是：康妮香<br />\n籤詩： 憔悴無人問 林間聽杜鵑 一聲山月笛 千里淚涓涓<br />\n解析： 多愁善感的人讀了這支簽，恐怕會氏落，非常失望。因為其間表達的意境似乎太寂寞，太悲哀，沒有給予一點點鼓舞，是嗎?其實不然，且聽我將意思一層層為你剖說。 你曾經受過不小的打擊和挫折，給身心伊健康帶來了嚴重的危害，如今處在艱難的歲月和處境中，沒有得到應有的關心和愛護，昔日的朋友們都已離去，你在凄清的林間聽那杜鵑聲悲啼，心都要碎了。 可是，終于從遠方傳來了召喚的山笛，在這美麗的夜色中，聲聲向人你呼喚。遠方的知音是那樣需要你。那位女性貴人，。雖然遠在千里，卻為你落下涓涓的淚水，遙寄著相思的感嘆。 不要再在原地自怨自艾，打點行裝，向西南方的遠方出吧!"},{"pid":"6c4b0ad7513dbfb224afd0510240943d3175934d","tid":837042,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"行杜鵑路線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcoc.com/record/2003/dujuan/dujuan_track.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcoc.com%2Frecord%2F2003%2Fdujuan%2Fdujuan_track.gif&h=eed31252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d2feaea0d2782bf7258399e6cd5e4f47bbdcde2","tid":837042,"uid":206416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c4b0ad7513dbfb224afd0510240943d3175934d","tid":837042,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"行杜鵑路線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcoc.com/record/2003/dujuan/dujuan_track.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcoc.com%2Frecord%2F2003%2Fdujuan%2Fdujuan_track.gif&h=eed31252&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"好難講真係好難預測<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daffbfc3e2f7a6022f211a5aba8a0e7e2f6a878b","tid":837042,"uid":133217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"93W起機先喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6fad94e39f535be0395d755aa87d507b37a89d","tid":837042,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"咁心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔一定叫康妮㗎，隨時叫玉兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2617f735fae89f179f3f3a023f7d06d039c0f305","tid":837042,"uid":206080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f6fad94e39f535be0395d755aa87d507b37a89d","tid":837042,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"咁心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔一定叫康妮㗎，隨時叫玉兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"Jma